- numbers_page = NumbersPage.new

- cache "numbers-fragment" do
  .typography.small-11.small-centered.medium-10.large-8
    %h1 Numbers
    .clearfix_left.column-block
      .translation_video{"data-ratio" => "0.75", style: "display: none;"}
        %video.video-js.vjs-default-skin{controls: "controls", controlslist: "nodownload", loop: "loop", preload: "metadata"}
          %source{src: "http://s3-ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/nzsl-assets/number-signs.mp4", type: "video/mp4"}
            %source{src: "http://s3-ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/nzsl-assets/number-signs.webm", type: "video/webm"}
      %a.button.translation_button{href: "javascript:void(0);"}
        %i.fi-play>
        Play this page in NZSL
    .rule_after.ckeditor_content
      %p
        Many numbers have alternate or varying forms in NZSL. Variation in numbers is linked to age, region, and personal
        preference of signers. New (Auslan) numbers were introduced into schools with Australasian Signed English in 1979,
        which differed from the number signs used by earlier generations.
      %p
        NZSL has several systems that incorporate number in which a number sign has a distinct movement and/or location
        including:
      %ul
        %li
          %a{href: "#cardinal"} Cardinal Numbers
          (counting)
        %li
          %a{href: "#ordinal"} Ordinal Numbers
          (ordering: 1st)
        %li
          %a{href: "#age"} Age
        %li
          %a{href: "#time"} Time
        %li
          %a{href: "#money"} Money
        %li
          %a{href: "#fractions"} Fractions
  .small-11.small-centered.medium-10.large-8
    .typography
      %h2#cardinal Cardinal Numbers
    / with divs because of IE7
    .typography
      %ul.no-bullet
        = render partial: "pages/number", collection: numbers_page.cardinal_numbers, as: :sign
    .typography
      %h2#ordinal Ordinal Numbers
    / with divs because of IE7
    .typography
      %ul.no-bullet
        = render partial: "pages/number", collection: numbers_page.ordinal_numbers, as: :sign
    .typography
      %h2#age Age
    / with divs because of IE7
    .typography
      %ul.no-bullet
        = render partial: "pages/number", collection: numbers_page.age_numbers, as: :sign
    .typography
      %h2#time Time
    / with divs because of IE7
    .typography
      %ul.no-bullet
        = render partial: "pages/number", collection: numbers_page.time_numbers, as: :sign
    .typography
      %h2#money Money
    / with divs because of IE7
    .typography
      %ul.no-bullet
        = render partial: "pages/number", collection: numbers_page.money_numbers, as: :sign
    .typography
      %h2#fractions Fractions
    / with divs because of IE7
    .typography
      %ul.no-bullet
        = render partial: "pages/number", collection: numbers_page.fractional_numbers, as: :sign
